      "side": 1,
      "message": "nit: naming -- \"running\" sounds like the opposite of \"idle,\" but it\u0027s actually the opposite of \"stopped,\" and \"busy\" is the opposite of \"idle.\"\n\nSome other options:\n - Stopped/Started\n - Dead/Alive\n - Disconnected/Connected",
