      "writtenOn": "2018-07-20T18:28:00Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I think we should use StopN and not worry about which bots are idle here. We will do a graceful shutdown, which means we\u0027ll wait for whatever tasks are running to finish. If our utilization indicates we need fewer bots, it doesn\u0027t really matter if those bots are running a 2-hour task, we still want them to stop after the task completes.",
